snippet.title: AND SHE SHALL BE BURNED UP WITH FIRE , BECAUSE יהוה ELOHIM WHO JUDGES HER IS MIGHTY  October 1, 2019
snippet.description:
#JusticeforBotham
#AmberGuygerGuilty

Rev 19:1 TS2009 And after this I heard a loud voice of a great crowd in the heaven, saying, “Halleluyah! Deliverance and esteem and respect and power to יהוה our Elohim! 
Rev 19:2 TS2009 “Because true and righteous are His judgments,  Psa. 19:9 because He has judged the great whore who corrupted the earth with her whoring. And He has avenged on her the blood of His servants shed by her.” Deu.32:43.

Rev 18:8 TS2009 “Because of this her plagues shall come in one day: death and mourning and scarcity of food. And she shall be burned up with fire, because יהוה Elohim who judges her is mighty.
